overview: Get ready for some wild horse backin', wild gun fightin' and old West Adventure and fun! Cactus Creek is the worst outlaw town in the Colorado territory.  Into this haven for outlaws ride Stormy, Texas, Cimaron and Logan (R.W. Hampton).  Will U.S. Marshal Trevor Cooper (Buck Taylor) arrive in time?  Filmed in beautiful high definition in the wilds of Colorado, Kansas, and Oklahoma this exciting, fun-filled tale of the old West is a must see for the entire family!
title: Cactus Creek
